

Things the program should do:
  Lock/Unlock Doors, Windows. 
  Open/Close garage door. 
  Turn on/Turn off different electronic devices(music, TVs, etc.)
  Alarm/Disarm security system. 

When you use the program: 
  1. At start it should propt you the password
      This password should be able to identify the person who is using the system. 
  2. It should set a time-stamp of when the program is used. 
  3. It should say where the program was used from. 
